data.description: Reduce your monthly payment with the assumable loan at a 4.875% interest rate!! Upon entering through the covered porch, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting living space that seamlessly combines the family room, dining area, and gourmet kitchen. The large island in the kitchen provides a convenient gathering place for family and friends to enjoy culinary delights and engage in lively conversation. The Caddo floor plan offers the perfect balance of privacy and comfort, with the owner's suite tucked away in the back right corner of the home. The luxurious primary bathroom features double vanities, a separate water closet, and a large walk-in closet, providing ample space for relaxation and rejuvenation. The laundry room is conveniently located across the hall from the owner's suite. Three additional bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home, connected by a secluded hallway and sharing a full bathroom. Each bedroom features a large closet with double doors.
